[SHORT DESC]
Prevents sleep. Increases wild encounters with higher level Pokémon.
[LONG DESC]
<p>This Pokémon cannot be put to sleep. Rest will fail when used by this Pokemon. If a Pokémon is sleeping, and then gains Insomnia, it is instantly cured of sleep.</p>

<p>When a Pokémon with this ability is first in the party, wild encounters with higher level Pokémon have a higher chance of occurring (relative to the highest level Pokémon normally seen in that area).</p>